    # --- Index page ---
    ("P6 is the current industrial prototype (Delijuice 870/970). Jiangxi (JX) factory with LTA; miniplant 8,160 L/h, 6 extractors. Each subsystem section includes a gallery of figures and, where filled in, component lists, interfaces, and design notes. Refer to <a href=\"Overview/\">Project overview</a> for the full subsystem list and context.", ("P6 为当前工业样机（Delijuice 870/970）。江西（JX）工厂与 LTA 合作；小型工厂 8,160 升/时，6 台压榨机。各子系统部分包含图示库，已填写处含部件列表、接口和设计说明。详见 <a href=\"Overview/\">项目概览</a> 获取完整子系统列表和背景。", "P6 é o protótipo industrial atual (Delijuice 870/970). Fábrica Jiangxi (JX) com LTA; miniplanta 8.160 L/h, 6 extratoras. Cada seção de subsistema inclui galeria de figuras e, quando preenchido, listas de componentes, interfaces e notas de design. Consulte <a href=\"Overview/\">Visão geral do projeto</a> para a lista completa de subsistemas e contexto.")),
    ("<strong>CAD colours:</strong> Colour keys are <strong>per subsystem</strong>. Each section has its own legend for the figures in that section. Use the legend on the relevant subsystem page when reading its CAD views.", ("<strong>CAD 颜色：</strong> 颜色说明<strong>按子系统</strong>。每个部分有其图示图例。阅读 CAD 视图时请使用相关子系统页面上的图例。", "<strong>Cores CAD:</strong> As legendas de cores são <strong>por subsistema</strong>. Cada seção tem sua própria legenda para as figuras. Use a legenda na página do subsistema relevante ao ler as vistas CAD.")),
    ("Use the links below to navigate. Sections <span class=\"badge ready\">with content</span> include CAD views and descriptions; <span class=\"badge\">skeleton</span> pages have thinner structure (may still include figures); <span class=\"badge\">to be completed</span> are placeholders for future detail.", ("请使用下方链接导航。<span class=\"badge ready\">有内容</span> 的部分包含 CAD 视图和描述；<span class=\"badge\">骨架页</span> 结构较简（可能仍含图示）；<span class=\"badge\">待完成</span> 为未来详情的占位符。", "Use os links abaixo para navegar. Seções <span class=\"badge ready\">com conteúdo</span> incluem vistas CAD e descrições; páginas <span class=\"badge\">esqueleto</span> têm estrutura mais fina (podem incluir figuras); <span class=\"badge\">a concluir</span> são placeholders para detalhes futuros.")),
    ("<strong>Frame → Loads and load paths</strong> — gallery + load discussion.", ("<strong>机架 → 载荷与载荷路径</strong> — 图示与载荷讨论。", "<strong>Estrutura → Cargas e caminhos de carga</strong> — galeria e discussão de cargas.")),
    ("<strong>Drivetrain &amp; transmission</strong> — full galleries, motor/reducer, gears/cam, both mount plates, yoke + drive-shaft figures.", ("<strong>传动系统与传动</strong> — 完整图示、电机/减速机、齿轮/凸轮、两块安装板、轭架与传动轴图。", "<strong>Acionamento e transmissão</strong> — galerias completas, motor/redutor, engrenagens/came, ambas placas de montagem, mancal e figuras de eixos.")),
    ("<strong>Extraction &amp; sync</strong> — main gallery; <strong>fruit support</strong>, <strong>peelers</strong>, <strong>driven bracket</strong> subpages with figures + contractor notes.", ("<strong>压榨与同步</strong> — 主图示；<strong>水果托架</strong>、<strong>削皮器</strong>、<strong>从动支架</strong> 子页面含图示与承包商备注。", "<strong>Extração e sincronização</strong> — galeria principal; subpáginas <strong>suporte de frutas</strong>, <strong>descascadores</strong>, <strong>suporte acionado</strong> com figuras e notas do contratado.")),
    ("<strong>Collection</strong> — main gallery; <strong>juice collection</strong> (collector/filter + side photos) and <strong>plungers &amp; filter</strong>.", ("<strong>收集</strong> — 主图示；<strong>果汁收集</strong>（收集器/过滤+侧视照片）和 <strong>柱塞与过滤</strong>。", "<strong>Coleta</strong> — galeria principal; <strong>coleta de suco</strong> (coletor/filtro + fotos laterais) e <strong>êmbolos e filtro</strong>.")),
    ("<strong>Fruit intake</strong> — main gallery; <strong>feeding subassembly</strong> (exploded + CIP/pusher/spring carousel), <strong>feeder body</strong> (iso + top), <strong>entry tubes</strong> (hinge + tube photos).", ("<strong>水果进料</strong> — 主图示；<strong>进料子组件</strong>（爆炸图+CIP/推杆/弹簧转盘）、<strong>进料器本体</strong>（等轴+俯视）、<strong>进料管</strong>（铰链+管照片）。", "<strong>Alimentação de frutas</strong> — galeria principal; <strong>subconjunto de alimentação</strong> (explosão + CIP/empurrador/carrossel de mola), <strong>corpo do alimentador</strong> (iso + topo), <strong>tubos de entrada</strong> (dobradiça + fotos de tubos).")),
    ("<strong>Core ejection</strong> — main gallery; <strong>plunger drive bracket</strong> (assembly CAD + iso/top/front) + <strong>side-panel drive</strong> (CAD + photos).", ("<strong>果芯弹出</strong> — 主图示；<strong>柱塞驱动支架</strong>（装配 CAD+等轴/俯视/正视图）+ <strong>侧板驱动</strong>（CAD+照片）。", "<strong>Ejeção de caroço</strong> — galeria principal; <strong>suporte de acionamento do êmbolo</strong> (CAD de montagem + iso/topo/frente) + <strong>acionamento do painel lateral</strong> (CAD + fotos).")),
